      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 337 to provide a remedy for employees misclassified as independent contractors; amend KRS 337.010 to define \"independent contractor\" and \"misclassified\"; repeal KRS 336.137, relating to marketplace contractors."
